title: Model received threats as kind gesture goes wrong
description: Beauty queen Alexandra Darby who has always been a patron for charity work, in these unprecedented times wanted to give something back to NHS by boosting morale and raising funds for the Dudley Group NHS Charity by singing to staff in the car park at Russells…
